  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/9be71ec3ed930b73475f77699973941e.poster.avif?t=1553732166\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/9be71ec3ed930b73475f77699973941e.webm?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/9be71ec3ed930b73475f77699973941e.mp4?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>CHECKMATE : Battle Arenas is turn based real time PvP game with new style. Kill your opponent’s King and get the highest Arena!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES OF THE CHECKMATE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy thrilling moments from turn based 1 vs 1 battle in real time.<br></li><li>Create your own deck with 20 skills in each hero and various units. <br></li><li>Break blocks in the map and make new strategy on your own.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/2142dfc51d61a944fa2ae07bc544cb4b.poster.avif?t=1553732166\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/2142dfc51d61a944fa2ae07bc544cb4b.webm?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/2142dfc51d61a944fa2ae07bc544cb4b.mp4?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bring your opponent close to you by breaking the block in the map. But, block direction is changed in each turn so make sure before you use this skill!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/0c27727c3ba6534a7a2cbb4a215ee587.poster.avif?t=1553732166\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/0c27727c3ba6534a7a2cbb4a215ee587.webm?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/0c27727c3ba6534a7a2cbb4a215ee587.mp4?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Checkmate! Shout out your win to the opponent by using unique hero skills and units with your style!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/9be71ec3ed930b73475f77699973941e.poster.avif?t=1553732166\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/9be71ec3ed930b73475f77699973941e.webm?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/9be71ec3ed930b73475f77699973941e.mp4?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>CHECKMATE : Battle Arenas is turn based real time PvP game with new style. Kill your opponent’s King and get the highest Arena!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES OF THE CHECKMATE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy thrilling moments from turn based 1 vs 1 battle in real time.<br></li><li>Create your own deck with 20 skills in each hero and various units. <br></li><li>Break blocks in the map and make new strategy on your own.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/2142dfc51d61a944fa2ae07bc544cb4b.poster.avif?t=1553732166\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/2142dfc51d61a944fa2ae07bc544cb4b.webm?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/2142dfc51d61a944fa2ae07bc544cb4b.mp4?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bring your opponent close to you by breaking the block in the map. But, block direction is changed in each turn so make sure before you use this skill!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/0c27727c3ba6534a7a2cbb4a215ee587.poster.avif?t=1553732166\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/0c27727c3ba6534a7a2cbb4a215ee587.webm?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970610/extras/0c27727c3ba6534a7a2cbb4a215ee587.mp4?t=1553732166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Checkmate! Shout out your win to the opponent by using unique hero skills and units with your style!",
